Key:[WHITE] Value:[#FFFFFF]
Key:[GREEN] Value:[#00FF00]
Key:[RED] Value:[#FF0000]
Unordered_map is now empty

Same, using only erase
Key:[BLACK] Value:[#000000]
Key:[BLUE] Value:[#0000FF]
Key:[RED] Value:[#FF0000]
Key:[GREEN] Value:[#00FF00]
Key:[WHITE] Value:[#FFFFFF]
Unordered_map is now empty
```

</p></details>

